title: Aug 18, 2022 - Mar-A-Lago Raid: Judge To Unseal Partial Affidavit, DOJ One Week To Respond
description:
MAR-A-LAGO UPDATE: the judge announced plans to reveal a partial affidavit, but the DOJ has one week to respond with redactions before the release. PRESIDENT BIDEN’S STASI: a new poll out of Rasmussen shows the Trump raid severely hurt voter trust in the FBI. NBC NEWS: new research suggests that monkeypox is field by sex between men, not skin on skin contact - classifying monkeypox as an STD. NYC 9/11 Tribute Museum has closed due to financial struggles, and the city government refuses to step up to help fund the museum.
